@startuml
title Phase 1D - Inverter Reading Capture and Generation Foundation

actor Technician
participant "Mobile App" as App
participant "Work Order API" as API
participant "InverterReadingService" as ReadingSvc
participant "GenerationCalculationService" as GenSvc
participant "ReportSummaryService" as ReportSvc
database "Operational DB" as DB

Technician -> App : Capture inverter photo + current reading
App -> API : Submit inverter reading
API -> ReadingSvc : validate and persist reading request
ReadingSvc -> DB : fetch latest finalized prior reading
DB --> ReadingSvc : previous reading or none

ReadingSvc -> GenSvc : compute delta/baseline/anomaly
GenSvc --> ReadingSvc : generation result

ReadingSvc -> DB : save reading snapshot
ReadingSvc --> API : success

== On report generation ==

App -> API : Request report data
API -> ReportSvc : build report summary
ReportSvc -> DB : load inverter readings for work order
ReportSvc -> GenSvc : aggregate site total generation
GenSvc --> ReportSvc : total generation
ReportSvc -> DB : persist report snapshot
ReportSvc --> API : report summary payload
API --> App : generation report data

note right of ReportSvc
Savings presentation is deferred to Phase 1E.
end note

@enduml
